      You can specify any field for encryption except the
      ``_id`` field.

#. If you are using :ref:`{+manual-enc+}
   <qe-fundamentals-manual-encryption>`, add a ``keyId`` field
   with the {+dek-abbr+} ID:

      :emphasize-lines: 4

      {
         path: "myDocumentField",
         bsonType: "int",
         queries: { queryType: "equality" }
      }

