.. _reshardCollection-to-same-key:

Reshard a Collection to the Same Shard Key
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

In order to reshard to the same shard key, set :ref:`forceRedistribution 
