Computing ``n`` Based on the Group Key for ``$group``
`````````````````````````````````````````````````````

You can also assign the value of ``n`` dynamically. In this example,
the :expression:`$cond` expression is used on the ``gameId`` field.

   :emphasize-lines: 11

